  <h2 id="about-work-heading">Analysis, engineering and adoption</h2>
  <p>My work sits between analysis and engineering. I clarify the question, resolve issues in metric definitions and source data, build the reporting, pipeline or workflow, and work with users until the solution is trusted and adopted.</p>
  <p>I work primarily with Power BI, SQL, Microsoft Fabric, Python, PySpark and Power Platform. I also use applied AI and Azure delivery patterns where they add practical value.</p>
  <p>The common thread is turning ambiguous operational problems into maintainable systems that support real decisions.</p>
</section>

